{{for|the genre|Electro (music)}} {{lowercase title}} {{Infobox music festival | name =electro-music | image = | caption = | location =[[Huguenot, Orange County, New York|Huguenot, New York]] | years_active =2005-present | founders = | dates = | genre = [[Electronic dance music]] | attendance = | capacity = | website =[http://electro-music.com/article.php?t=49018 Electro-music Festival] }}
The '''electro-music''' [[music festival]] is a festival and conference devoted to [[experimental electronic music]] .<ref>"[http://electro-music.com/article.php?t=49018 electro-music 2011 - Sept 9-11 - Huguenot, NY]".</ref> Since 2005 it has been held in [[Huguenot, Orange County, New York|Huguenot, New York]]. The annual electro-music festival, known as the "Woodstock of electronic music," bills itself as "the world's premiere event for experimental electronic music". The gathering features three days of electronic music concerts, seminars, workshops, demonstrations, jam sessions, video art, a laptop battle, and a swap-meet.
