ue]], American actor and activist, founded [[Do Something]] * 1967 &ndash; [[Lili Taylor]], American actress * 1967 &ndash; [[Tom Waddle]], American football player and sportscaster *[[1969]] &ndash; [[Kjell Ove Hauge]], Norwegian school principal and track and field athlete * 1969 &ndash; [[Siniša Mihajlović]], Serbian footballer and manager * 1969 &ndash; [[Danis Tanović]], Bosnian director and screenwriter *[[1971]] &ndash; [[Calpernia Addams]], American actress, author, and activist * 1971 &ndash; [[Jari Litmanen]], Finnish footballer * 1971 &ndash; [[Joost van der Westhuizen]], South African rugby player (d. 2017) *[[1972]] &ndash; [[Neil Primrose (musician)|Neil Primrose]], Scottish drummer *[[1974]] &ndash; [[Karim Bagheri]], Iranian footballer and manager *[[1975]] &ndash; [[Liván Hernández]], Cuban baseball player * 1975 &ndash; [[Brian Littrell]], American singer-songwriter and actor * 1975 &ndash; [[Niclas Wallin]], Swedish ice hockey player *[[1977]] &ndash; [[Stephon Marbury]], American basketball player * 1977 &ndash; [[Gail Kim]], Canadian professional wrestler *[[1978]] &ndash; [[Lauren Ambrose]], American actress and producer *[[1980]] &ndash; [[Imanol Harinordoquy]], French rugby player * 1980 &ndash; [[Luis Gabriel Rey]], Colombian footballer *[[1981]] &ndash; [[Tony Hibbert]], English footballer * 1981 &ndash; [[Fred Jackson (American football)|Fred Jackson]], American football player *[[1982]] &ndash; [[Jason Hirsh]], American baseball player *[[1983]] &ndash; [[José Morales (catcher)|Jose Morales]], Puerto Rican-American baseball player * 1983 &ndash; [[Justin Verlander]], American baseball player *[[1984]] &ndash; [[Brian McCann (baseball)|Brian McCann]], American baseball player * 1984 &ndash; [[Trevor Noah]], South African comedian, actor, and television host * 1984 &ndash; [[Ramzee Robinson]], American football player *[[1985]] &ndash; [[Ryan Sweeney]], American baseball player * 1985 &ndash; [[Julia Volkova]], Russian singer and actress * 