=== 10 April ===
The spokesman of the Ukrainian operational headquarters reported in the morning that pro-Russian forces had opened fire on 35 occasions on Ukrainian positions the previous day<!--3 WIA--><ref name=MoD6am04-10>{{cite web|url=http://www.mil.gov.ua/news/2018/04/10/zvedennya-pres-czentru-shtabu-ato-za-dobu-9-kvitnya-2018-roku/ |title=Зведення Прес-центру штабу АТО за добу 9 квітня 2018 року |trans-title=Information by ATO HQ on 9 April 2018 |date=10 April 2018 |accessdate=10 April 2018 |publisher=MoD |language=uk}}</ref> (including on 32 occasions in Donetsk region and on 3 occasions in Luhansk region<ref name=noon04-10ru/>); the fire was returned on 9 occasions.<ref name=noon04-10ru/> The spokesman of the Ministry of Defence confirmed at noon that three Ukrainian servicemen were wounded in action in the Donbass region on 9 April.<ref name=noon04-10ru>{{cite web|url=http://uacrisis.org/ru/65995-gutsulyak-48 |title=Боевики применили 122-мм артиллерию и минометы – полковник Гуцуляк |trans-title= |date=2018-04-10 |accessdate=2018-04-10 |publisher=MoD |language=ru |website=uacrisis.org}}</ref> Pro-Russian authorities at Donetsk city recorded 21 Ukrainian violations of the ceasefire in 11 locations using small arms, snipers, heavy machine guns, automatic grenade launchers, 73&nbsp;mm antitank recoilless rifles, 82&nbsp;mm mortars, 120&nbsp;mm mortars and 122&nbsp;mm self-propelled artillery.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://dnr-online.ru/vsu-za-sutki-21-raz-narushili-rezhim-prekrashheniya-ognya-stskk/|title=ВСУ за сутки 21 раз нарушили режим прекращения огня — СЦКК {{!}} Официальный сайт ДНР|date=2018-04-10|work=Официальный сайт ДНР|access-date=2018-04-10|language=ru-RU}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://dnr-online.ru/vsu-otkryli-ogon-iz-tyayazhelogo-vooruzheniya-po-n-p-leninskoe-stskk/|title=ВСУ открыли огонь из тяяжелого вооружения по н.п. Ленинское — СЦКК {{!}} Официальный сайт ДНР|date=2018-04-09|work=Официальный сайт ДНР|access-date=2018-04-09|language=ru-RU}}</ref>

According to the information provided by the JFO press-centre in the evening, as of 6:00&nbsp;pm pro-Russian forces had opened fire on positions of Ukrainian troops on 22 occasions, one Ukrainian serviceman was wounded.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/ato.news/posts/1917625814914882 |title=Зведення Прес-центру штабу АТО станом на 18.00 10 квітня 2018 року |trans-title= |date=2018-04-10 |accessdate=2018-04-10 |publisher=Press-centre of the ATO HQ |language=uk}}</ref> In the surroundings of Donetsk city, pro-Russian tanks engaged Ukrainian redoubts at Pisky and Kamianka. Rebel troops fired 120&#160;mm mortars at Avdiivka, Pisky, Butivka coal mine and Kamianka. Butivka also came under 82&#160;mm mortar fire. Infantry weapons and rocket launchers were employed to attack Ukrainian troops at Avdiivka, Kamianka, Krasnohorivka, Novotroitske, Butivka, Opytne and Marinka. Armoured fighting vehicles shelled Pisky, and antitank guided missiles were fired at Krasnohorivka. In the region of Mariupol, pro-Russian tanks opened fire on Ukrainian positions at Vodiane. Berdyansk, Lebedinske, Shyrokyne and Vodiane received 120&#160;mm mortar fire, while Lebedinske and Talakivka were hit by 82&#160;mm mortar rounds. Ukrainian troops at Lebedinskye Starohnativka, Talakivka, Hnutove, Vodiane, and Pavlopil came under small arms and heavy machine gun fire. Antitank guided missiles landed in Hnutove and Shyrokyne. In the northern section of the demarcation line, rebel forces fired small arms, heavy machine guns and 82&#160;mm mortars at Novooleksandrivka. Armoured fighting vehicles opened fire at Luhanske. By the end of the day the number of registered ceasefire violations had risen to 64, three more Ukrainian soldiers were wounded and one was injured.<ref name=MoD6am04-11/> Pro-Russian authorities told the press that Ukrainian forces pounded their forces at Volvo Center, Dokuchaievsk, Spartak, Trudivske, Zabicheve, Oktyabrivsky coal mine and Mineralne, in the surroundings of Donetsk city, and Sakhanka, Uzhivka, Pikuzy and Petrovske, in the region of Mariupol. The Ukrainian military used small arms, sniper rifles, heavy machine guns, automatic grenade launchers, 73&nbsp;mm antitank recoilless rifles, 82&nbsp;mm mortars, 120&nbsp;mm mortars, BMP-1 and BMP-2 armoured vehicles. In the main incidents, Uzhivka came under 120&nbsp;mm mortar fire, while Sakhanka and Trudivske were shelled with 82&nbsp;mm mortars. Ukrainian BMP-1 and BMP-2 armoured vehicles from Bohdanivka engaged pro-Russian redoubts at Petrovske supported by 82&nbsp;mm mortar fire. The industrial area of Volvo Center was hit by 152&nbsp;mm artillery barrages.<ref>• [https://dnr-online.ru/vsu-otkryli-minometnyj-ogon-po-prigorodu-donetska-stskk/ВСУ открыли минометный огонь по пригороду Донецка — СЦКК {{!}} Официальный сайт ДНР].<br />• [https://dnr-online.ru/vsu-veli-ogon-po-donetsku-stskk/ ВСУ вели огонь по Донецку — СЦКК / AFU shelled Donetsk — JCCC {{!}} Официальный сайт ДНР].<br />• [https://dnr-online.ru/pod-obstrelom-vsu-shahta-oktyabrskij-rudnik-i-kominternovo-stskk/ Под обстрелом ВСУ шахта «Октябрьский рудник» и Коминтерново – СЦКК {{!}} Официальный сайт ДНР].<br />• [https://dnr-online.ru/vsu-otkryli-ogon-po-n-p-petrovskoe-stskk-4/ ВСУ открыли огонь по н.п. Петровское — СЦКК {{!}} Официальный сайт ДНР].<br />• [https://dnr-online.ru/vsu-otkryli-ogon-po-n-p-petrovskoe-stskk-3/ ВСУ открыли огонь по н.п. Петровское — СЦКК {{!}} Официальный сайт ДНР].<br />• [https://dnr-online.ru/utrom-vsu-obstrelivali-spartak-stskk/ Утром ВСУ обстреливали Спартак — СЦКК {{!}} Официальный сайт ДНР].<br />• [https://dnr-online.ru/vsu-otkryli-ogon-po-n-p-sahanka-stskk-4/ ВСУ открыли огонь по н.п. Саханка — СЦКК {{!}} Официальный сайт ДНР].</ref> Other sources reported tank and 152&nbsp;mm artillery fire in the western outskirts of Donetsk city later in the night. In the self-proclaimed Luhansk People's Republic, 82&nbsp;mm and 120&nbsp;mm mortar fire was reported at Smile and Kalynove-Borshchevate.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news-front.info/2018/04/10/vsu-nachali-massirovannyj-obstrel-donetska/|title=ВСУ НАЧАЛИ МАССИРОВАННЫЙ ОБСТРЕЛ ДОНЕЦКА|last=|first=|date=10 April 2018|website=News-Front|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=10 April 2018}}</ref>

=== 11 April ===
According to the information provided by the spokesman of the Ukrainian operational headquarters in the morning, pro-Russian troops had opened fire on 64 occasions on Ukrainian positions the previous day<!--4 WIA, 1 injured--><ref name=MoD6am04-11>{{cite web|url=http://www.mil.gov.ua/news/2018/04/11/zvedennya-pres-czentru-shtabu-ato-za-dobu-10-kvitnya-2018-roku/ |title=Зведення Прес-центру штабу АТО за добу 10 квітня 2018 року |trans-title= |date=2018-04-11 |access-date=2018-04-11 |publisher=Press-centre of the ATO HQ |language=uk}}</ref> (including on 60 occasions in Donetsk and on 4 occasions in Luhansk region<ref name=noon04-11ru/>); the fire was returned on 19 occasions.<ref name=noon04-11ru/> The spokesman of the Ministry of Defence confirmed at noon that four Ukrainian servicemen were wounded and one was injured in the Donbass region on 10 April.<ref name=noon04-11ru>{{cite web|url=http://uacrisis.org/ru/66013-gutsulyak-49 |title=Боевики совершили 64 обстрелов, активно применяли танки, тяжелые минометы – полковник Гуцуляк|trans-title= |date=2018-04-11 |accessdate=2018-04-11 |publisher=MoD |language=ru |location= [[Kiev]] }}</ref> Pro-Russian officials at Donetsk city recorded 28 Ukrainian violations of the ceasefire in 11 different areas using small arms, snipers, heavy machine guns, automatic grenade launchers, 73&nbsp;mm antitank recoilless rifles, 82&nbsp;mm mortars, 120&nbsp;mm mortars, armoured personnel vehicles, armoured fighting vehicles and 152&nbsp;mm self-propelled artillery. Three civilian residents were wounded.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://dnr-online.ru/vsu-za-sutki-28-raz-narushali-peremirie-stskk/|title=ВСУ за сутки 28 раз нарушали перемирие – СЦКК {{!}} Официальный сайт ДНР|date=2018-04-11|work=Официальный сайт ДНР|access-date=2018-04-11|language=ru-RU}}</ref> According to local officials, Ukrainian forces attacked pro-Russian positions at Zholobok, Kalynivka, Kalynove and Kalynove-Borshchevate, within the boundaries of the self-proclaimed Luhansk People's Republic. The Ukrainian army employed small arms, heavy machine guns, automatic grenade launchers, 73&nbsp;mm antitank recoilless rifles, 82&nbsp;mm mortars and BMP-1 armoured vehicles. One pro-Russian soldier was wounded.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://goves.net/news/1345-svodka.html|title=сводка|website=Социальная сеть Новороссии|access-date=2018-04-11}}</ref>

The press-centre of the JFO reported in the evening that as of&nbsp;6:00 pm pro-Russian troops had opened fire on Ukrainian troops on 13 occasions, exclusively in Donetsk region, no casualties were reported.<ref name=":6">{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/ato.news/posts/1918717104805753 |title=Зведення Прес-центру штабу АТО станом на 18.00 11 квітня 2018 року |trans-title= |date=11 April 2018 |accessdate=11 April 2018 |publisher= |language=uk|website=www.facebook.com/ato.news/posts}}</ref> In the region of Donetsk, Ukrainian forces at Pisky were attacked with heavy machine guns, rocket launchers, 82&nbsp;mm mortars, 120&nbsp;mm mortars and armoured fighting vehicles. Pro-Russian tanks engaged Ukrainian redoubts at nearby Kamianka, while antitank rockets landed in Avdiivka and Marinka, where Ukrainian troops were harassed with small arms and sniper fire. In the region of Mariupol, rebel forces fired grenade launchers at Talakivka and heavy machine guns at Pavlopil, Hnutove and Vodiane. Small arms fire was reported also at Hnutove and Vodiane. In the northern sector of the demarcation line, small arms fire was reported at Stanytsia Luhanska. Troitske was meanwhile hit by 120&#160;mm mortar fire. By the end of the day the number of registered ceasefire violations had risen to 38.<ref name=MoD6am04-12/><ref name=":6" /> Early in the morning the Ukrainian military shelled eight areas around Donetsk city using 73&nbsp;mm antitank recoilless rifles, 82&nbsp;mm mortars, 120&nbsp;mm mortars, antiaircraft artillery, BMP-2 armoured vehicles and 122&nbsp;mm self-propelled guns.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://dnr-online.ru/ukrainskie-siloviki-utrom-podvergli-massirovannomu-obstrelu-territoriyu-respubliki-stskk/|title=Украинские силовики утром подвергли массированному обстрелу территорию Республики — СЦКК / Ukrainian military subjected the territory of the Republic to massive shelling in the morning — JCCC {{!}} Официальный сайт ДНР|date=2018-04-11|work=Официальный сайт ДНР|access-date=2018-04-11|language=ru-RU}}</ref> Natural gas pipelines were damaged at the district of Kuybishev. Seven civilian residents were wounded.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://dnr-online.ru/gk-donbassgaz-prinimaet-ekstrennye-mery-po-likvidatsii-posledstvij-artobstrela-donetska/|title=ГК "Донбассгаз" принимает экстренные меры по ликвидации последствий артобстрела Донецка (видео) / Donbassgaz SC takes urgent measures to eliminate consequences of the artillery strike on Donetsk (video) {{!}} Официальный сайт ДНР|date=2018-04-11|work=Официальный сайт ДНР|access-date=2018-04-11|language=ru-RU}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://dnr-online.ru/stskk-privodit-utochnennye-dannye-po-obstrelu-so-storony-vsu/|title=СЦКК приводит уточненные данные по обстрелу со стороны ВСУ {{!}} Официальный сайт ДНР|date=2018-04-11|work=Официальный сайт ДНР|access-date=2018-04-11|language=ru-RU}}</ref> Later in the day, Ukrainian forces attacked Yakovliivka, Kruta Balka, Petrovsky district, Dokuchaievsk, Abakumove coal mine, [[Staromykhailivka]] and Spartak, in the area of Donetsk city, and Zaitseve, in the outskirts of Horlivka. In the main incidents, BMP-1 armoured vehicles opened fire on pro-Russian positions at Spartak supported by 82&nbsp;mm mortar fire, while Kruta Balka and Abakumove coal mine were hit by 82&nbsp;mm mortar fire.<ref>• [https://dnr-online.ru/vsu-otkryli-ogon-po-yakovlevke-stskk/ ВСУ открыли огонь по Яковлевке — СЦКК / AFU opened fire on Yakovlevka — JCCC {{!}} Официальный сайт ДНР].<br />• [https://dnr-online.ru/vsu-otkryli-ogon-po-krutoj-balke-stskk-2/ ВСУ открыли огонь по Крутой Балке — СЦКК].<br />• [https://dnr-online.ru/vsu-otkryli-ogon-po-petrovskomu-rajonu-donetska-stskk-5/ ВСУ открыли огонь по Петровскому району Донецка — СЦКК / AFU opened fire on Petrovsky district of Donetsk — JCCC].<br />• [https://dnr-online.ru/vsu-otkryli-ogon-po-dokuchaevsku-stskk-4/ ВСУ открыли огонь по Докучаевску — СЦКК / AFU opened fire on Dokuchayevsk — JCCC ]<br /> • [https://dnr-onlin